---

<header class="glass fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 mb-8 pb-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-3 border-b border-glass-border backdrop-blur-md gap-2 sm:gap-0">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:items-start">
    <span class="font-mono text-codex-accent text-base sm:text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">MKP-TRI â€” Living Codex</span>
